Package checker.sourceparser

Interface Summary
SourceParser Interface for a source file language type.
 

Class Summary
CppSourceParser CppSourceFileParsing takes c/c++ source file content and parses it for comments and references.
JavaSourceParser JavaSourceFileParser takes java source file content and parses it for comments and references.
ParserComments ParserComments scans source code comments and writes them to array.
PHPSourceParser PHPSourceFileParsing takes php source file content and parses php code sections for comments and references.
ReferenceProcessing This class is for processing references.
SourceParserFactory Class for creating SourceParser instances.
SourceParserLine SourceParserLine is a one source code line including required positions for source code parsing.
TemplateSourceParser This a template for new source code parser.
